ted":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b54217242c8a8b3c31ee7f5a5955","msg_type":"text","content":"[OK]","sender":{"id":"ou_35fb190135a668a941cf060191cd58e0","sender_type":"user","name":"何杰"},"create_time":"2026-03-11T19:36:41+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b542177d4c8a8b4a1d23d00cbcdf","msg_type":"text","content":"还在项目这没回去","sender":{"id":"ou_0cbe05a0b8d7f0425e8661c119cefcea","sender_type":"user","name":"王文强"},"create_time":"2026-03-11T19:35:45+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b5421769548b0b36878c4d205ea5","msg_type":"image","content":"![image](img_v3_02vm_cca00c92-ce89-49fc-b7ff-524d611fd36g)","sender":{"id":"ou_0cbe05a0b8d7f0425e8661c119cefcea","sender_type":"user","name":"王文强"},"create_time":"2026-03-11T19:35:33+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true},{"message_id":"om_x100b5421787bfcb4b27cda26474d0a9","msg_type":"text","content":"后面单独加备注，评论。这两天安排的事有些满","sender":{"id":"ou_0cbe05a0b8d7f0425e8661c119cefcea","sender_type":"user","name":"王文强"},"create_time":"2026-03-11T19:35:07+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b542157b3c0a0b275a8927239cf2","msg_type":"text","content":"写外勤拜访记录的格式，我看了一下大家的打卡，除了范景昊的都不符合标准，从明天开始不符合打卡标准的不算有效拜访@王文强 @王垣皓","sender":{"id":"ou_35fb190135a668a941cf060191cd58e0","sender_type":"user","name":"何杰"},"create_time":"2026-03-11T19:27:20+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"ou_0cbe05a0b8d7f0425e8661c119cefcea","name":"王文强"},{"key":"@_user_2","id":"ou_0a41155c9f7ed341a3c314470ad4768c","name":"王垣皓"}]},{"message_id":"om_x100b54215e4e7ca0b396b256bf5beb7","msg_type":"post","content":"1. 拜访目的：明确本次外勤拜访的核心目标。\n2. 过程描述：简要梳理拜访全程，重点说明拜访时间、拜访对象、核心沟通内容。\n3. 关键结果：提炼本次拜访的核心成果、达成的事项。\n4. 下一步计划：明确后续工作安排，明确完成时间、具体动作，确保可落地、可跟踪。","sender":{"id":"ou_35fb190135a668a941cf060191cd58e0","sender_type":"user","name":"何杰"},"create_time":"2026-03-11T19:24:56+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b5426c198dc80c39f99a40b90755","msg_type":"text","content":"收到","sender":{"id":"ou_0cbe05a0b8d7f0425e8661c119cefcea","sender_type":"user","name":"王文强"},"create_time":"2026-03-11T16:33:57+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b5426c01f60b4b2eafb2cb407bd8","msg_type":"text","content":"收到","sender":{"id":"ou_0a41155c9f7ed341a3c314470ad4768c","sender_type":"user","name":"王垣皓"},"create_time":"2026-03-11T16:33:49+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b5426c27630bcc2dcf34bf5e3a58","msg_type":"text","content":"@_all 周五下午4点开始和锐捷对新建摸底的进展，之前分配给大家的新建项目，已经责任到人让大家去现场看了。如果还没有做覆盖的，这两天安排时间去现场实地勘察一下，这是年前就给的项目机会了，别到时候问项目情况一点也不知道","sender":{"id":"ou_35fb190135a668a941cf060191cd58e0","sender_type":"user","name":"何杰"},"create_time":"2026-03-11T16:33:15+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b5425c426c080b492f0965291a07","msg_type":"text","content":"收到","sender":{"id":"ou_0a41155c9f7ed341a3c314470ad4768c","sender_type":"user","name":"王垣皓"},"create_time":"2026-03-11T15:24:31+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b54399d2db044b271e4e993655b7","msg_type":"text","content":"我给刘晓说了，你提个流程","sender":{"id":"ou_0cbe05a0b8d7f0425e8661c119cefcea","sender_type":"user","name":"王文强"},"create_time":"2026-03-11T11:10:54+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b5439862a78a4b34124f9da7b34d","msg_type":"text","content":"@王垣皓 阿特拉斯的走个开票申请吧","sender":{"id":"ou_0cbe05a0b8d7f0425e8661c119cefcea","sender_type":"user","name":"王文强"},"create_time":"2026-03-11T11:07:58+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"ou_0a41155c9f7ed341a3c314470ad4768c","name":"王垣皓"}]},{"message_id":"om_x100b54398b40f0a0b3c57f867d702ca","msg_type":"image","content":"![image](img_v3_02vm_b051c059-1f61-47e1-ab16-b5d80b92d1fg)","sender":{"id":"ou_0cbe05a0b8d7f0425e8661c119cefcea","sender_type":"user","name":"王文强"},"create_time":"2026-03-11T11:07:05+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true},{"message_id":"om_x100b543fd0344ca8b21561d049b6b6b","msg_