{"type":"message","id":"c797d930","parentId":"faebb932","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:26:27.705Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"员工版已发送，供姚总预览。","thinkingSignature":"98bcfcc1004c6c35cc2d5d1a6b5a1d06bf6f3c46cb5d185e8f2abf2fbb6fefec"},{"type":"text","text":"已发送员工版预览，请您确认。\n\n如确认无误，我将通过机器人身份发送到销售顾问沟通群。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":60459,"output":34,"cacheRead":41378,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101871,"cost":{"input":0.0181377,"output":0.000040799999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0012413399999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01941984}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774103185049}}
{"type":"message","id":"ce554639","parentId":"c797d930","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:31:05.606Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-21 22:31:04 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | 姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b) [msg:om_x100b54def4b138a4c3ab5f53edcd4e0]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54def4b138a4c3ab5f53edcd4e0\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"sender\": \"姚霖\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-21 22:31 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"name\": \"姚霖\"\n}\n```\n\n之前说过员工版直发点评和内容和总分就行了，而且周五有销售晨会，周例会是周一开，只有周一没有销售晨会，怎么记不住呢，把这些落实到记忆和技能里面，不要再犯错了"}],"timestamp":1774103465600}}
{"type":"message","id":"517860c5","parentId":"ce554639","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:31:32.239Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"姚总指出两个问题：\n\n1. 员工版格式问题：之前说过员工版只需要直发点评内容和总分，不需要那么多内容\n2. 晨会/周例会逻辑错误：周五有销售晨会，周例会是周一开，只有周一没有销售晨会\n\n我需要：\n1. 立即修正记忆，更新MEMORY.md中的规则\n2. 更新技能文件 SKILL.md\n3. 承认错误，保证不再犯\n\n立即去修改MEMORY.md和技能文件。","thinkingSignature":"788ab9192175a8033ed2dea688dd9f4075588416f5bc3d4f1067ea685d2317bd"},{"type":"text","text":"收到姚总批评，立即修正！\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mx2bxx83s0lc_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/MEMORY.md","oldText":"### 特殊说明（双休）\n- 周一：获取周五日报（周例会无晨会）\n- 周二：不获取周一晨会（周无一晨会）\n- 其他工作日：正常获取昨日日报+晨会","newText":"### 特殊说明（双休）\n- **周五有销售晨会**（不是周例会）\n- 周一：获取周五日报（周一没有销售晨会）\n- 周二：不获取周一晨会（周一没有销售晨会）\n- 其他工作日：正常获取昨日日报+晨会\n\n### 员工版格式要求（刚性要求）\n- 只需包含：**点评内容 + 总分**\n- 无需包含：原文引用、详细评分明细、各项得分拆解"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":137,"output":315,"cacheRead":100974,"cacheWrite":982,"totalTokens":102408,"cost":{"input":0.000041099999999999996,"output":0.00037799999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0030292199999999996,"cacheWrite":0.00011783999999999998,"total":0.0035661599999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774103465603}}
{"type":"message","id":"75b20442","parentId":"517860c5","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:31:32.448Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_mx2bxx83s0lc_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/MEMORY.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 236 6. **销售标准**：每天至少3次拜访，不足3次必须批评\n 237 7. **售前标准**：每天至少5个报价项目\n 238 \n 239 ### 特殊说明（双休）\n-240 - 周一：获取周五日报（周例会无晨会）\n-241 - 周二：不获取周一晨会（周无一晨会）\n+240 - **周五有销售晨会**（不是周例会）\n+241 - 周一：获取周五日报（周一没有销售晨会）\n+242 - 周二：不获取周一晨会（周一没有销售晨会）\n 242 - 其他工作日：正常获取昨日日报+晨会\n 243 \n+245 ### 员工版格式要求（刚性要求）\n+246 - 只需包含：**点评内容 + 总分**\n+247 - 无需包含：原文引用、详细评分明细、各项得分拆解\n+248 \n 244 ### 核心规则（必须遵守）\n 245 1. 鼓励与鞭策各占一半\n 246 2. 销售晨会承诺必须检查（仅销售岗位）\n 247 3. 未写经验沉淀要指出\n     ...","firstChangedLine":240},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774103492346}}
{"type":"message","id":"919b7c8a","parentId":"75b20442","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:31:37.950Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在更新技能文件。","thinkingSignature":"d6a703b7eea4aaff26e0d1fc788bd0a90224d206a70bd7190f4f7c5b4b4c25bc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pusrps06uujy_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/skills/daily-report-review/SKILL.md","oldText":"### 特殊说明（双休）\n- 周一：获取周五日报（周例会无晨会）\n- 周二：不获取周一晨会（周无一晨会）\n- 其他工作日：正常获取昨日日报+晨会","newText":"### 特殊说明（双休+节假日）\n- **周五有销售晨会**（不是周例会）\n- **周例会周一开**，只有周一没有销售晨会\n- 周一：获取周五日报（因为周一没有销售晨会）\n- 周二：不获取周一晨会\n- 其他工作日：正常获取昨日日报+晨会"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":61064,"output":191,"cacheRead":41378,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102633,"cost":{"input":0.0183192,"output":0.0002292,"cacheRead":0.0012413399999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01978974}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774103492446}}
