\": \"后面单独加备注，评论。这两天安排的事有些满\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_0cbe05a0b8d7f0425e8661c119cefcea\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王文强\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-11T19:35:07+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b542157b3c0a0b275a8927239cf2\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"写外勤拜访记录的格式，我看了一下大家的打卡，除了范景昊的都不符合标准，从明天开始不符合打卡标准的不算有效拜访@王文强 @王垣皓\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_35fb190135a668a941cf060191cd58e0\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"何杰\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-11T19:27:20+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"ou_0cbe05a0b8d7f0425e8661c119cefcea\",\n          \"name\": \"王文强\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_2\",\n          \"id\": \"ou_0a41155c9f7ed341a3c314470ad4768c\",\n          \"name\": \"王垣皓\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54215e4e7ca0b396b256bf5beb7\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"1. 拜访目的：明确本次外勤拜访的核心目标。\\n2. 过程描述：简要梳理拜访全程，重点说明拜访时间、拜访对象、核心沟通内容。\\n3. 关键结果：提炼本次拜访的核心成果、达成的事项。\\n4. 下一步计划：明确后续工作安排，明确完成时间、具体动作，确保可落地、可跟踪。\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_35fb190135a668a941cf060191cd58e0\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"何杰\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-11T19:24:56+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5426c198dc80c39f99a40b90755\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"收到\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_0cbe05a0b8d7f0425e8661c119cefcea\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王文强\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-11T16:33:57+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5426c01f60b4b2eafb2cb407bd8\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"收到\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_0a41155c9f7ed341a3c314470ad4768c\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王垣皓\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-11T16:33:49+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5426c27630bcc2dcf34bf5e3a58\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@_all 周五下午4点开始和锐捷对新建摸底的进展，之前分配给大家的新建项目，已经责任到人让大家去现场看了。如果还没有做覆盖的，这两天安排时间去现场实地勘察一下，这是年前就给的项目机会了，别到时候问项目情况一点也不知道\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_35fb190135a668a941cf060191cd58e0\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"何杰\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-11T16:33:15+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5425c426c080b492f0965291a07\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"收到\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_0a41155c9f7ed341a3c314470ad4768c\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王垣皓\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-11T15:24:31+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54399d2db044b271e4e993655b7\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"我给刘晓说了，你提个流程\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_0cbe05a0b8d7f0425e8661c119cefcea\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王文强\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-11T11:10:54+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5439862a78a4b34124f9da7b34d\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@王垣皓 阿特拉斯的走个开票申请吧\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_0cbe05a0b8d7f0425e8661c119cefcea\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王文强\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-11T11:07:58+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"ou_0a41155c9f7ed341a3c314470ad4768c\",\n          \"name\": \"王垣皓\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54398b40f0a0b3c57f867d702ca\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"image\",\n      \"content\": \"![image](img_v3_02vm_b051c059-1f61-47e1-ab16-b5d80b92d1fg)\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_0cbe05a0b8d7f0425e8661c119cefcea\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王文强\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-11T11:07:05+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b543fd0344ca8b21561d049b6b6b\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"system\",\n      \"content\": \"\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-11T08:40:15+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b543f1bd58870b3fcd8555c428ae\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"video_chat\",\n      \"content\": \"<meeting>📹 销售顾问沟通群的视频会议\\n🕙 2026-03-11 08:29</meeting>\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_35fb190135a668a941cf060191cd58e0\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"何杰\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-11T08:29:05+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b543f3bd538a4c2910881f1e4e16\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"system\",\n      \"content\": \"Meeting has started. New messages will be synced in the group chat and in-meeting chat.\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-11T08:29:05+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x1